rows.label: qst720201_msg0001
rows.name:
So where are these traces
of Metsu the 4th Squad found?

rows.label: qst720201_msg0002
rows.name:
They say it's Valfum Hill,
inland from the Ordia Great Plain.

rows.label: qst720201_msg0003
rows.name:
That's all the info we have.
We'll just have to go and check
it out ourselves.

rows.label: qst720201_msg0004
rows.name:
From here,
it might even be closer than the harbor.

rows.label: qst720201_msg0006
rows.name:
Along the way,
please tell us the stories
of your travels, Adel.
